{"id": "art-2462", "label": "Art. 2462", "title": "Art. 2462", "slug": "art-2462", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_350699915\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1760\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_350699915\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 246<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_815507518\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1759\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_815507518\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>În cazul unei diviz&#259;ri în care <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in</span> împreun&#259; toate <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>/<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nsociale ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> divizate <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> toate celelalte valori mobiliare ce confer&#259;\ndrept de vot în adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndivizate, nu este necesar&#259; aprobarea diviz&#259;rii de c&#259;tre adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> divizate\ndac&#259;:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1016457474\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1758\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1016457474\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)au fost îndeplinite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span>\nde publicitate a proiectului de divizare prev&#259;zute la art. 242 cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o lun&#259; înainte ca divizarea s&#259;\nproduc&#259; efecte;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_78232343\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1757\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_78232343\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)pe o perioad&#259; de o lun&#259; înaintea datei de la\ncare <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> produce efecte <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> implicate în divizare au putut\nconsulta documentele prev&#259;zute la art. 244 alin. (1). <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 244 alin. (3)-(5) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1727541374\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1756\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1727541374\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)au fost îndeplinite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span>\nde informare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a organelor de administrare/conducere a\ncelorlalte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> implicate în <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>, prev&#259;zute la art. 243<sup>2</sup>\nalin. (4).</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}